  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Our study aimed to examine a possible association between Restless legs syndrome and
      cerebrovascular disease, by examining patients during hospitalization for acute stroke or
      transient ischemic attack, in a matched case-control design.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
